title: The Settle Down Cafe
typeOfFood: International, Western, Salad bar, Take-out, Non-veg
description: Serves meat, veg options available. Small cafe off Westgate Rd and near Central Station. Around half the menu is vegetarian and looks like sandwiches could be made to order (ask) with hummus, falafel, salsa, caramelized onion, roasted veggies, etc. Offers a selection of veggie salads including bok choi & sesame, and chickpea & spinach. Fair trade coffee and other drinks.
